  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"position:relative;height:120px;overflow:hidden\"><img alt=\"Portal Books bar.jpg\" src=\"/images/0/07/Portal_Books_bar.jpg\" width=\"1480\" height=\"120\" /><div style=\"position:absolute;max-width:100%; left:500px; top:30px; font-size:120%;\"><div class=\"hlist hlist-separated\"><ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Books</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Portal:Characters\" title=\"Portal:Characters\">Characters</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Timeline_of_major_events\" title=\"Timeline of major events\">History</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Portal:Culture\" title=\"Portal:Culture\">Culture</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">Chapter summaries</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Portal:Geography\" title=\"Portal:Geography\">Geography</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Houses_of_Westeros\" title=\"Houses of Westeros\">Houses</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Portal:TV_Show\" title=\"Portal:TV Show\">TV Series</a></li></ul></div></div></div>\n<table style=\"width:100%; color:#666;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" height=\"20px\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:50%; vertical-align:text-top; padding: 5px 10px 10px 5px;\">\n<div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\">\n<p>This portal is dedicated to any Books published about, or in anyway related to <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i>, his <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:High fantasy\">epic fantasy</a> novel series, and its universe.\n</p>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\"><img alt=\"Grey-bg rounded.png\" src=\"/images/f/fa/Grey-bg_rounded.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"25\" />\n<div style=\"position:absolute; left:15px; top:2px;\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em; margin-top: -0.15em;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"George_R._R._Martin\">George R. R. Martin</span></h2></div></div>\n<div style=\"padding-left:15px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:10px;\">\n<p><i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i> series by George R. R. Martin, consisting of five published volumes:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (1996)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (1998)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (2000)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (2005)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (2011)</li></ul>\n<p>The planned remaining two novels are titled:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dream_of_Spring\" title=\"A Dream of Spring\">A Dream of Spring</a></i></li></ul>\n<p>Additionally there are also three prequel novellas, set in the same world, roughly ninety years before the main events, commonly known as the \"<a href=\"/index.php/Dunk_and_Egg\" title=\"Dunk and Egg\">Tales of Dunk and Egg</a>\" after their main protagonists:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (1998)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (2003)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (2010)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i> (2015) (collection of the first three novellas)</li></ul>\n<p>Three novellas based on chapter sets from the books:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"Blood of the Dragon\">Blood of the Dragon</a></i> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asimov%27s_Science_Fiction\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Asimov&#39;s Science Fiction\">Asimov’s</a>, July 1996).</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Path_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"Path of the Dragon\">Path of the Dragon</a></i> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asimov%27s_Science_Fiction\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Asimov&#39;s Science Fiction\">Asimov’s</a>, December 2000).</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Arms_of_the_Kraken\" title=\"Arms of the Kraken\">Arms of the Kraken</a></i> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dragon_(magazine)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dragon (magazine)\">Dragon</a> issue 305, August 2002).</li></ul>\n<p>Three novellas, prequels based on <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen, or, The Blacks and the Greens</a></i> (2013)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince, or, A King's Brother</a></i> (2014)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (2017)</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\"><img alt=\"Grey-bg rounded.png\" src=\"/images/f/fa/Grey-bg_rounded.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"25\" />\n<div style=\"position:absolute; left:15px; top:2px;\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding:.15em .4em; margin-top: -0.15em;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Other\">Other</span></h2></div></div>\n<div style=\"padding-left:15px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:10px;\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, a boxed collection of twelve <i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i> map posters, stretching from Westeros to Asshai. (2012)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\"><i>The World of Ice &amp; Fire: The Untold History of Westeros and the Game of Thrones</i></a>, a companion volume to the <i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i> novels. (2014)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (comics)\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i> comics</a>, adaptation of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>. (2011 – ongoing)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Feast of Ice and Fire\">A Feast of Ice and Fire</a></i>, a cookbook of recipes derived from dishes and meals from Westeros and Essos. (2012)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Groans\" title=\"A Game of Groans\">A Game of Groans</a></i>, a parody of <i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i>. (2012)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall_(book)\" title=\"Beyond the Wall (book)\"><i>Beyond the Wall</i></a>, a collection of essays exploring the series' influences and narrative choices. (2012)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, a history of the Targaryen dynasty from <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency of Aegon III</a>. (2018)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i>, an abridged version of <i>Fire &amp; Blood</i> with new illustrations. (2022)</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left; position:relative; left:0px; top:2px; margin:0;\"><img alt=\"Grey-bg rounded.png\" src=\"/images/f/fa/Grey-bg_rounded.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"25\" />\n<div style=\"position:absolute; left:15px; top:2px;\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold; border-bottom:none; font-size:130%; padding: .15em .4em; margin-top: -0.15em;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summaries\">Summaries</span></h2></div></div>\n<div style=\"padding-left:15px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:10px;\">\n<p>Check out our chapter by chapter <a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">Book Summaries</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a> series. <br />(YES, it's obviously spoiler heavy. Don't say we didn't warn you!)\n</p>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;vertical-align:top;\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-spacing: 10px; text-align: center; color: #4284B0; font: bold 1.2em/1.5em Georgia, &#39;Bookman Old Style&#39;, Serif; font-style: italic; border-left: 4px solid #4284B0;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"background: #EFEFEF;\">\n<td colspan=\"12\" style=\"padding: 5px 10px 5px 20px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #FAFAFA;\">\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 33%; padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">A Game of Thrones\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 33%; padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">A Clash of Kings\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 33%; padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">A Storm of Swords\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #FAFAFA; border-bottom: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\"><img alt=\"Cover - A Game of Thrones.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/39/Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg/100px-Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/39/Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg/150px-Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/39/Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg/200px-Cover_-_A_Game_of_Thrones.jpeg 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\"><img alt=\"Cover - A Clash of Kings.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c1/Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg/100px-Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c1/Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg/150px-Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c1/Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg/200px-Cover_-_A_Clash_of_Kings.jpeg 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\"><img alt=\"Cover - A Storm of Swords.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/72/Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg/100px-Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/72/Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg/150px-Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/72/Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg/200px-Cover_-_A_Storm_of_Swords.jpeg 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #FAFAFA;\">\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF; width: 25%;\">A Feast for Crows\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">A Dance with Dragons\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\">The Winds of Winter\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-top: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF; width: 25%;\">A Dream of Spring\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #FAFAFA;\">\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\"><img alt=\"Cover - A Feast for Crows.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e0/Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg/100px-Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e0/Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg/150px-Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e0/Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg/200px-Cover_-_A_Feast_for_Crows.jpeg 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\"><img alt=\"Cover - A Dance with Dragons.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a4/Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg/100px-Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a4/Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg/150px-Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a4/Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg/200px-Cover_-_A_Dance_with_Dragons.jpeg 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\"><img alt=\"Winds of winter.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/42/Winds_of_winter.jpg/99px-Winds_of_winter.jpg\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/42/Winds_of_winter.jpg/148px-Winds_of_winter.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/42/Winds_of_winter.jpg/198px-Winds_of_winter.jpg 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; border-right: 1px solid #EFEFEF;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dream_of_Spring\" title=\"A Dream of Spring\"><img alt=\"Nocover.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Nocover.png/96px-Nocover.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Nocover.png/144px-Nocover.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/48/Nocover.png/192px-Nocover.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: left;background: #EFEFEF; border-bottom: 2px solid #FAFAFA;\">\n<td colspan=\"12\" style=\"padding: 5px 10px 5px 20px;\">“A mind needs books as a sword needs a whetstone, if it is to keep its edge.”\n<div style=\"float:right;\">&#160;—&#160;A Game of Thrones</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: left;background: #EFEFEF;\">\n<td colspan=\"12\" style=\"padding: 5px 10px 5px 20px;\">“The best fantasy is written in the language of dreams. It is alive as dreams are alive, more real than real ... for a moment at least ... that long magic moment before we wake.”\n<div style=\"float:right;\">&#160;—&#160;George R. R. Martin</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122610\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.041 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.076 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 32/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 171/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 710/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   43.019      1 Template:Hlist\n100.00%   43.019      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7574-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403122610 and revision id 326425\n -->\n",
